title: Walking with dinosaurs in Kalasin
text:
Walking with dinosaurs in Kalasin 11 Aug 2015 at 11:04 430 viewed 0 comments - + Sirindhorn Dinorsaur museum features the most complete fossilised skeleton of a dinosaur found so far in Southeast Asia. On Mother's Day this year (Aug 12) it will have an exhibit of moving dinosaurs.
